<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in St. Andrews Heights</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">St. Andrews Heights Community Association operates a community hall, complete with a standard kitchen, wheelchair access, and meeting rooms. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The City of Calgary operates tennis courts, a soccer field, playing field and a baseball diamond. The association also offers Sports, fitness and seniors programs. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Kensington hosts Salsa Festival in July and Christmas in Kensington Village in December. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Shopping in Kensington is varied, with art stores (fitting for its proximity to ACAD), unique clothing boutiques, and other accessories. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Kensington is also home to the Plaza Theatre, known for its showings of independent films, cult classics, and locally made films.</p>

        </div>
